data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT*** Discover the epitome of modern living in this beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom end-unit townhome nestled in this adorable neighborhood. This home boasts a seamless blend of contemporary design and functionality, featuring a gorgeously updated interior and cozy rooms flooded with natural light. The unfinished portion of the basement, prepped for a bathroom addition, offers endless possibilities for expansion or customization. Step into the serene fenced in private  backyard with a generous deck and paved lower level patio, providing an ideal space for outdoor gatherings or quiet relaxation. With its prime location and stylish upgrades, this townhome stands as a true gem in its class and one of the nicest homes in the community.
